## Study Path

!!! note "Recommended Approach"
    Follow the curriculum modules in order — they respect prerequisite dependencies and build knowledge progressively.

1. Start with the [Curriculum](curriculum.md) to understand the learning path
2. Work through [Study Notes](study_notes.md) for each module
3. Use [Revision Resources](revision.md) for quick review
4. Test yourself with [Practice Questions](questions.md)
5. Take the [Mock Exam](mock_exam.md) to assess readiness
6. Review the [Gap Report](gap_report.md) and address weak areas
7. Check your [Readiness Assessment](readiness.md) before scheduling the exam
